parameters: \N<Aniki>So, where's Miyazaki? Can't see him anywhere.
\N<Aniki>Don't you think you're being a bit rude?

\N<Yasu>Do you think you can get away with just apologizing, you
bastard?!

\N<Aniki>Well, never mind. Shall we continue? You're the one who laid
hands on my woman, right?
\N<Aniki>So, what are you going to do?

\N<Aniki>What are you going to do to make things right? You don't
think a simple apology will suffice, do you?
\N<Naoto>Hey, hey... Please stop with the violence...!

\N<Aniki>Ah, that might be good too, huh? But there might be a quicker
way, don't you think?

\N<Aniki>You understand, don't you? As a resolution for this incident,
pay me 1 million yen. Then we'll settle this.

\N<Aniki>What? So, you're saying I can just kidnap this person right
now?
\N<Yasu>What are you going to do, Miyazaki!?
\N<Naoto>Y-Yeah! Asking for 1 million yen for something like that....

\N<Aniki>Is that all you think it is? Are you saying that messing with
my woman is just something trivial?

\N<Aniki>This strong-willed girl. She's your woman, right? Should I
violate her right in front of you and give you a trauma to remember?
\N<Aniki>Could it be that you've already experienced it? Ahahaha!!

\N<Aniki>Huh? I have business with Miyazaki. The woman should stay out
of it.
\N<Kaede>If you had been quiet and listened earlier...

\N<Kaede>It's ridiculous to demand 1 million just because she was
touched.

\N<Kaede>It's this guy's fault for laying hands on your girlfriend,
but demanding 1 million yen is just too much!

\N<Yasu>What do you mean too much? He laid hands on Aniki's woman, you
know!!
\N<Kaede>Miya, how much can you afford to pay now?
\N<Miya>Um... um... around 100,000 yen... I can pay that much...
\N<Aniki>Hey, woman. You have experience in martial arts, right?

\N<Aniki>The kick you gave to Yasu and me. It was clearly not the
movement of an amateur.
\N<Aniki>I'll violate you here as you wish...
\N<Aniki>Oh? What's wrong? Are you scared now...
\N<Kaede>There's no way that earlier was serious.
\N<Aniki>Damn it! Stop moving around so much...!!!

\N<Kaede>Phew... What are we going to do? Are we still going to
continue?
\N<Kaede>If you're not satisfied, then let's do it thoroughly.
\N<Miya>Um... This... I'm really sorry about it.
\N<Naoto>Ah, now that I'm relieved, my back hurts.....
\N<Naoto>But, I didn't know Kaede was this strong...
\N<Kaede>Well, I've been doing karate all the time, so...
\N<Miya>No one could beat Kaede, including adults.
\N<Kaede>Don't you have something to say first?
\N<Kaede>Ah, this is already the second time I've helped you.
\N<Naoto>Eh? There was another time before this?

\N<Miya>Ah, yes. Back when I was being bullied by senior members at
the dojo, Kaede came to my rescue....
\N<Kaede>You've always been running away from everything, haven't you?
\N<Miya>Because I don't like pain either, you know...?

\N<Naoto>Haha. But anyway, I'm glad everything turned out well, Miya-
kun.
\N<Miya>Yes! With this, I can live in this village without worries.

\N<Naoto>Eh? But now that there's no need to worry about being chased,
there's no need for me to stay in this village either....
\N<Miya>Well, I was able to do that a little... haha.

\N<Kaede>You'll probably get bored again and go back to the city,
right?

\N<Miya>Well, that might be true, but until then, take care of
yourself. Haha.
\N<Kaede>Just make sure you don't cause any trouble.

\N<Naoto>Well then, let's continue to take care of each other from now
on, Miya-kun!

\N<Miya>Ah! By the way, for this time, please let me thank you in some
way!!

\N<Miya>Yes! I wonder what would have happened if Naoto-san and Kaede
weren't here...

\N<Miya>There's a beach nearby, right? Let's have a luxurious barbecue
there! I'll treat you to everything!!
\N<Kaede>You're treating us... but didn't you run out of money?
\N<Miya>Oh, actually I had 150,000 yen from the beginning... Haha.
